txt.en: Precious timber awaits those who brave the hidden dangers of the ethereal crevasse of Clovengap.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest.</rgb>
'What is this? You have slain a vicious beast of the Clovengap? I praise you for your efforts and your talents, [placeholder].'

'Hidden within the crevasse of Clovengap is the precious resource of lumber. The journey there is not an easy one, however, we need the lumber there for our restoration efforts. Are you willing to take on this task?'\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest. This quest can be completed with one or two adventurers.</rgb>
You should return to Zádokh Flint-eye and apprise him of your efforts.
